summary: Ego vehicle is approaching an intersection on a rainy day. A pedestrian in a yellow raincoat is standing near the crosswalk. A cyclist suddenly appears from behind the pedestrian and falls in the crosswalk.
actions: Ego vehicle is moving forward. Other vehicles are present in the distance. Pedestrian is standing. Cyclist is riding and then falls.
next_action: Ego vehicle will likely need to brake to avoid collision with the cyclist.
